Detailed Description

cvmx_gser::_slice::_qsgmii_mode

These registers are for diagnostic use only. These registers are reset by hardware only during chip cold reset. The values of the CSR fields in these registers do not change during chip warm or soft resets.

Slice 1 does not exist on GSER4, GSER5, or GSER6.
